Ghana’s Government to Buy Shares in Shelter Afrique, Times Says

-- B y   M o s e s   M o z a r t   D z a w u
-- 
2011-06-17T10:14:09Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-17/ghana-s-government-to-buy-shares-in-shelter-afrique-times-says.html
Ghana ’s government plans to buy a
minimum of $10 million shares in  Shelter Afrique , a Nairobi-
based mortgage provider, to help local companies secure finance
for housing projects, The Ghanaian Times reported.  Lawmakers approved the purchase, which entitles the West
African nation to a seat on the board of the lender, the Accra-
based newspaper said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at 
 asguazzin@bloomberg.net . 